### Parallel Tool Call Optimization

For improved efficiency and user experience, recommendations:

1. **Mark first task as in-progress when creating** - When creating task list with todo_create, set first pending task status to in_progress, start execution immediately
2. **Start processing in same batch of tool calls** - After creating todo, start processing first task in the same batch of tool calls

When in doubt, use this tool. Proactive task management demonstrates your thoroughness, ensuring you successfully complete all requirements.
